##PDF to Excel Converter

## Project Overview

This project extracts structured information from PDF files and converts it into Excel spreadsheets automatically using Python.

## Features

* Extracts data from PDF files
* Converts extracted information into Excel (.xlsx)
* Processes multiple PDF files
* Modular project structure

## Technologies Used

* Python
* PyMuPDF
* OpenPyXL

## Project Structure

* config/
* excel/
* extractors/
* input_pdfs/
* main.py

## How to Run

1. Install the required packages.
2. Place PDF files inside the `input_pdfs` folder.
3. Run:

```bash
python main.py
```

4. Excel files will be generated inside the `output_excel` folder.

## Note

Sample input PDF files are not included because they are proprietary. Users can place their own PDF files in the `input_pdfs` folder.
